{"tid":774121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再有內地人庭上拍照被捕","createTime":"2018-08-10T05:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T05:12:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cdcbb383ae59861863a37f977efd467b1f533098","tid":774121,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:24:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180810/20472980\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180810%2F20472980&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=72d208d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180810%2F20472980&h=d75790bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180810/20472980</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月10日 <br />\n<br />\n再有內地人庭上拍照被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180810/large/10la9p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F10la9p21.jpg&h=bb737f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地男昨日涉於九龍城裁判法院庭內拍攝被扣查。溫文學攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】再有人公然在法院拍照被捕。一名內地男子昨午到九龍城法院，上庭替僱主繳交稅項罰款，其間他聲稱要即場向僱主報告行蹤，在法院內外及庭上拍照，被旁聽人士揭發舉報，最後被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱向僱主報告行蹤<br />\n<br />\n被捕的姓張男子持雙程證來港，據稱在一間科技公司任職。昨午3時許他涉嫌在九龍城裁判法院6樓的3號法庭上用手機拍照，被旁聽人士發現向庭警舉報後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n有人報稱是替僱主上庭繳交稅項罰款，需向僱主匯報行蹤，遂拍下在法庭的相片。現場消息稱，有人之前到達法院後，先在法院外拍了一張照片，即時傳給僱主。之後他來到6樓的法庭門口又拍一張，再傳給僱主。<br />\n<br />\n當他進入3號法庭後，據知當時該庭準備審理一宗商業稅款案件，但正等候開庭，法官仍未進入法庭內，有人拍下庭內照片時被揭發。警方在事主手機內發現三張相關相片。<br />\n今年5月，內地女子唐琳玲在高院第28庭內拍照，被判藐視法庭罪成囚7日，之後被遣返內地。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫文學  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n聯招收生不過半港大醫科走數　議員：對基層學生不公<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n居屋凱樂苑管理費$935"},{"pid":"5afc3d1722b79350a243981aba8b364096646b85","tid":774121,"uid":198943,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:38:14.000Z","msg":"禾係腥移民,禾唔識法律<br />\n但是禾認該沒有犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e866d40c3e0ffcb6ab9cb330cf6c4f1eb64894","tid":774121,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5afc3d1722b79350a243981aba8b364096646b85","tid":774121,"uid":198943,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:38:14.000Z","msg":"禾係腥移民,禾唔識法律<br />\n但是禾認該沒有犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識法律就冇犯法 <br />\n新移民係最威！"},{"pid":"51b3fbf07855bf160c053daa8b625b4a87530bfa","tid":774121,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b08d56e797e153ac0ac5c5384858ef7d67a673","tid":774121,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"我唔撚識法律"},{"pid":"a79d4de01813d9536e3033f15d5ca75807bb2ca4","tid":774121,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"黃大仙人？<br />\n內你老母地"},{"pid":"59ea60cfabbdce047d6c5f2c3327720181322f0a","tid":774121,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"放得幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07db545e2e078263d0d53e43e165ebd81fa6615b","tid":774121,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b96a70261f7c51d255e193e3d022615b1c25378","tid":774121,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike